{"name":"Hymn if Glorious Perseverance","type":"spell","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally within 60 feet would be reduced to 0 Hit<br />Points or die.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>As long as you keep singing, your allies won’t fall. Instead of being knocked out or dying, the triggering ally recovers [[/r 1]]{Hit Point} and gains 50 temporary Hit Points, but it cannot benefit from other healing effects until your composition ends. When the composition ends, the target loses all remaining HP and temporary HP and goes back to dying.</p>\n<p>If you have the Rapturous Finale feat and haven’t used it today, you can use it and then cast hymn of glorious perseverance as part of the same reaction.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The temporary Hit Points increase by 5.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.sinclairs-library-playtest.sinclairs-library-effects.q4PS8gHSLxpxUzZY]{Effect: Hymn of Glorious Perseverance}</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.819,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-02-13T16:52:46.226-06:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.7.4"}}},"traits":{"value":["bard","composition","healing"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":8},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"necromancy"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":"An Ally"},"range":{"value":"60 ft."},"area":null,"time":{"value":"Reaction"},"duration":{"value":"Sustained up to 1 minute."},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"ability":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"heightening":{"type":"interval","interval":1,"damage":{}}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"XvAQTyKnzb1d2fbp":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.YNscD2sZCZwBlZYZ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.7.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676328766229,"modifiedTime":1676838016856,"lastModifiedBy":"XvAQTyKnzb1d2fbp"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"ECQmyh7W2jxDMW6R"}
{"name":"Earth Warp","type":"spell","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Touching a natural stone surface connected to the earth, like the side of a mountain or the wall of an underground cavern, you and the spell’s other targets melt into the stone and can travel through the earth at breakneck speeds so long as you remain in physical contact with one another. As a group, you have a burrow Speed of 60 feet while navigating spaces that require fine control of your movement, or a travel Speed of 100 miles per hour over wider areas. Though blind, you and any creatures you bring with you have a general sense of direction, knowing which way is magnetic north (if applicable), which way is down, and how far away and in what direction the nearest surface is. While in this state, you do not need to breathe, cannot speak, and may communicate telepathically with the creatures you brought along with you. If at any point you or one of the creatures accompanying you exit the earth, the spell ends, placing all affected creatures in the nearest unoccupied space to the creature that exited first.</p>\n<p>If a creature breaks physical contact or the duration of the spell ends before a creature willingly exits the earth, they take [[/r 10d6[force]]] damage and are shunted out of the earth into the nearest unoccupied space. If a target of the spell is carrying a creature in an extradimensional space, the spell fails.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.819,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-02-07T14:16:36.647-06:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.7.1"}}},"traits":{"value":["earth"],"rarity":"rare"},"level":{"value":7},"spellType":{"value":"attack"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":["primal"]},"school":{"value":"transmutation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":"you and up t