{"name":"Read and Reload","type":"spell","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You keep an eye on your enemies’ weaknesses as your hands put stone to sling. Recall Knowledge about a creature you can see, learning one weakness it has if you succeed in addition to any other information you would gain, then Interact to reload a sling you’re wielding</span> </p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.827,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-02-27T02:51:45.490-06:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.8.1"}}},"traits":{"value":["magus"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":1},"spellType":{"value":"attack"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"divination"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":null,"time":{"value":"1"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"ability":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"8zmVfjhSMQSSGSg8":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.VfeCD8sbLAX3KX3h"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.8.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1677487905495,"modifiedTime":1677488258843,"lastModifiedBy":"8zmVfjhSMQSSGSg8"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"e402IxyGEuo2Iza4"}
{"name":"Requiem of Fire and Steel","type":"spell","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You play a song of unfinished business in order to bring an end to the restless. You and all allies in the area gain the benefits of the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.JQdwHECogcTzdd8R]{Ghost Touch} property rune on weapon attacks and unarmed strikes.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (6th)</strong> You and your allies’ spells also gain the<br />benefits of the ghost touch property rune.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.819,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-02-13T12:09:42.204-06:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.7.4"}}},"traits":{"value":["bard","cantrip"],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":3},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"necromancy"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":{"value":60,"type":"emanation"},"time":{"value":"1"},"duration":{"value":"1 Round"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"ability":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"heightening":{"type":"interval","interval":3,"damage":{}}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"XvAQTyKnzb1d2fbp":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9nH99vaVhVhKm2Id"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.7.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676311782207,"modifiedTime":1676331296752,"lastModifiedBy":"XvAQTyKnzb1d2fbp"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"qG4sDWncdHPFjzZ9"}
